{"tid":2284753,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載］有無人試過新嗰隻omni餐肉，又有新證據指佢係藍","createTime":"2020-11-13T14:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T17:10:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f38de8c3d5fc7d64718dc065044050965cff6d3c","tid":2284753,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">好失望，明明個老闆david有喺612、616出聲，之後又有參加大三罷，但轉個頭又進軍bug bug shop同贊助TVB班偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Green Common (佢隻Omni餐肉最近好出名) 一直係受爭議商戶，雖然上年有參與大罷工，但又同TVB關係糾纏不清，首先執行總監係有撐警前科嘅TVB親生女陳貝兒，第二加盟咗Big Big Shop，而根據線人報料，Green Common亦經常向偽人贊助產品。<br />\n<br />\n現在係時候畀Green Common選擇，到底係要與香港人同行，同紅媒割蓆，定係留喺BBS助紂為虐。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">今日係派慘任務，大家唔好搞錯，已經見到好多人派錯嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n <p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">😢 Green Common (素食) 😢</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greencommon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreencommon&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5cf29ace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greencommon</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/OmniPork\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOmniPork&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=6e46ff09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/OmniPork</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CG8Qf1n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCG8Qf1n.png&h=5ec2a92e&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">無綫電視立場偏頗，新聞部扭曲事實，懇請 貴公司棄用Big Big Shop銷售產品，並停止向其偽人提供產品贊助，免使紅媒得益。本人尊重 貴公司的市場推廣策略，但基於良心消費原則，本人只能無奈地杯葛Green Common及其旗下食品，並呼籲朋友及家人抵制。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">【抵制 TVB戰線及抵制名單】</span></span></strong><br />\nFollow 抵制TVB戰線，每日派嬲，對方廣告費就億億聲咁跌！<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=4fb321b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ROdDNVHyXzVsy4zgZ15TpTCo8e-wUiUHnB1XNDejOFQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ROdDNVHyXzVsy4zgZ15TpTCo8e-wUiUHnB1XNDejOFQ&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=3a5611ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ROdDNVHyXzVsy4zgZ15TpTCo8e-wUiUHnB1XNDejOFQ</a> </span></p></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c91bd3407ec6cc4facefbcdb4cbf506d5e78bc63","tid":2284753,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"原post<br />\n<br />\n有無人試過新嗰隻omni餐肉，又有新證據指佢係藍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2284688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2284688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2088cde00590adfff532412be177eed071a9a46","tid":2284753,"uid":258894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1e41c32e9b268e128d843961a90155fbef43d1","tid":2284753,"uid":141668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:26:38.000Z","msg":"藍唔藍唔清楚，淨係知肥到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02af37ba2b42f6c11752ac604f18703eea58cd8","tid":2284753,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"直接比嬲